msgid "1300:でも、中に入ったからっていきなり殺されるっていうことはない。[linebreak]それは間違いない。[%p]"
msgstr "1300:But the one thing I was sure of was that she wouldn't just kill me the second I walked inside. I could be totally confident of that.[%p]"

msgid "1400:だって、ここは渋谷のど真ん中。ハチ公像の目の前だ。[%p]"
msgstr "1400:This was the middle of Shibuya. We were right in front of Hachiko.[%p]"

msgid "1500:周囲にはたくさん人がいる。[linebreak]衆人環視の中で僕を殺せば、セナにとっては自殺行為だ。[%p]"
msgstr "1500:There were hundreds of people around us.[%p]"

msgid "1600:僕は一度深呼吸すると、意を決して電車の中へと足を踏み入れた。[%p]"
msgstr "1600:Killing me in front of all these people would be suicide for Sena. I took a deep breath, and stepped inside the train car.[%p]"

msgid "1700:思わず立ち止まってしまった。[%p]"
msgstr "1700:Suddenly, I stopped.[%p]"

msgid "1800:今この瞬間にもディソードで襲いかかってこられたらどうしよう。[%p]"
msgstr "1800:What if she suddenly leaped at me with her Di-Sword?[%p]"

msgid "1900:そう考えると怖くてたまらない。[%p]"
msgstr "1900:The idea scared me to death.[%p]"

msgid "2000:僕は恐怖心に負け、セナの言葉に従いそうになる。[%p]"
msgstr "2000:I'd be so terrified, I'd probably do whatever she wanted me to.[%p]"

msgid "2100:一歩、車内に足を踏み入れた。[%p]"
msgstr "2100:I took another step inside the car.[%p]"

msgid "2200:でもそこで、すぐに考え直した。[%p]"
msgstr "2200:But then I stopped again.[%p]"

msgid "2300:これじゃセナの思うつぼだ。[%p]"
msgstr "2300:This was just what Sena wanted me to do.[%p]"

msgid "2400:飛んで火にいる夏の虫。[linebreak]蜘蛛の巣に絡め取られた羽虫。[%p]"
msgstr "2400:I was like a moth to a flame. Or a moth caught in a spider's web, or something.[%p]"

msgid "2500:ダメだ……。[linebreak]自分から進んで死地に赴いてどうする。[linebreak]逃げるべきだ。逃げた方がいい。[%p]"
msgstr "2500:This wasn't safe. What was I doing, walking right to my death? I should run. Running would be much safer.[%p]"

msgid "2600:あの鎖からも分かる通り、この女はとんでもない怪力の持ち主だ。[%p]"
msgstr "2600:I could tell from the chain that she was incredibly strong.[%p]"

msgid "2700:ちょっと腕をひねられただけで、[linebreak]僕は為す術なく地面に組み伏せられ、[linebreak]腕をあっさりと折られるだろう。[%p]"
msgstr "2700:She could just twist her hand a little... and drop me helplessly to the ground, breaking my arm.[%p]"

msgid "2800:しかもそれだけじゃない。[%p]"
msgstr "2800:And that wasn't all.[%p]"

msgid "2900:この女はディソードまで持っている。[%p]"
msgstr "2900:She had a Di-Sword, too.[%p]"

msgid "3000:あんな太くて巨大な剣で斬りつけられたら、即死だ。[%p]"
msgstr "3000:If that huge, heavy sword hit me, I'd be dead.[%p]"

msgid "3100:この女はここで僕を待ち構えていた。[linebreak]なにかを企んでいる。[%p]"
msgstr "3100:She'd been waiting for me. She was planning something.[%p]"

msgid "3200:今すぐ逃げろ……！[%p]"
msgstr "3200:I had to get out of here, now![%p]"

msgid "3300:外に出ようと、その場で踵を返す。[%p]"
msgstr "3300:I turned around to run.[%p]"

msgid "3400:[name]拓巳[line]「な……」[%p]"
msgstr "3400:[name]拓巳[line]What?[%p]"

msgid "3500:いつの間にか出入り口の扉が“閉まっていた”――[%p]"
msgstr "3500:But the door to the train was... closed.[%p]"

msgid "3600:たった今、僕が入ってきたばかりで。[linebreak]まだほんの数秒も経っていない。[linebreak]なのに――[%p]"
msgstr "3600:I'd only just come in. Just a few seconds had passed. So why...[%p]"

msgid "3700:音もなく、[linebreak]気配もなく、[linebreak]扉は、無情にも閉まっていた。[%p]"
msgstr "3700:Without a sound, without any sign, had the door been able to close?[%p]"

msgid "3800:立ちすくむ。[linebreak]なにが起きたか、すぐには理解できない。[%p]"
msgstr "3800:I just stood there helplessly. I couldn't understand what had happened.[%p]"

msgid "3900:いつ、このドアは閉じた？[linebreak]誰が、閉めた？[%p]"
msgstr "3900:When had the door closed? Who had shut it?[%p]"

msgid "4000:自動で開閉するとは思えない。[linebreak]それに自動ドアだとしても閉まるときの音は聞こえるはず。[%p]"
msgstr "4000:That wasn't an automatic door. And even if it was, I would've heard a noise when it closed.[%p]"

msgid "4100:セナはシートに腰を下ろしたまま微動だにしていない。[%p]"
msgstr "4100:Sena had been sitting on her seat, not moving at all.[%p]"

msgid "4200:だから閉めたのは彼女じゃない。[%p]"
msgstr "4200:It hadn't been her.[%p]"

msgid "4300:当然だけど僕も閉めていない。[linebreak]扉に手すら触れていない。[%p]"
msgstr "4300:And of course, it wasn't me, either. I hadn't even touched it.[%p]"

msgid "4400:この電車の管理者らしき人物が近くにいるのかと思ったけど、窓の外にそれらしい姿は見当たらない。[%p]"
msgstr "4400:I wondered if the manager of the car car might be somewhere nearby, but I looked outside the window and didn't see anyone who looked like that.[%p]"

msgid "4500:いや、この際誰が閉めたのかはどうでもいい。[%p]"
msgstr "4500:No, wait. It didn't matter who'd shut the door.[%p]"

msgid "4600:僕は、車体の奥にあるもうひとつの出入り口へと視線を移した。[%p]"
msgstr "4600:I looked toward the door at the other end of the car.[%p]"

msgid "4700:そっちの扉も、閉まっている。[%p]"
msgstr "4700:It was closed, too.[%p]"

msgid "4800:――閉じ込められた。[%p]"
msgstr "4800:—I was locked in.[%p]"

msgid "4900:車内には僕とセナだけ。[linebreak]それがなにを意味するのか。[%p]"
msgstr "4900:The only people in the car were Sena and me. What did that mean?[%p]"

msgid "5000:いろいろなネガティブな想像が頭の中を巡り、悲鳴を上げそうになる。[%p]"
msgstr "5000:A thousand negative thoughts came to me, and made me want to scream.[%p]"

msgid "5100:[name]セナ[line]「いつまで――」[%p]"
msgstr "5100:[name]セナ[line]How long…[%p]"

msgid "5200:セナがやっぱり僕をにらみつけたまま、また声を発する。[%p]"
msgstr "5200:Sena spoke, glaring at me.[%p]"

msgid "5300:[name]セナ[line]「そこに突っ立っているつもりだ？」[%p]"
msgstr "5300:[name]セナ[line]Are you going to keep standing there?[%p]"

msgid "5400:[name]拓巳[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "5400:[name]拓巳[line]...[%p]"

msgid "5500:逃げ道は、ない。[linebreak]足が震える。[%p]"
msgstr "5500:There was nowhere to run. My legs were shaking.[%p]"

msgid "5600:騒げば外の人は気付くかもしれないけど、僕がここから脱出するより先にセナにフルボッコにされるだろう。[%p]"
msgstr "5600:If I made a lot of noise, the people outside might notice, but before they could intervene, Sena would kick the crap out of me.[%p]"

msgid "5700:ひとまずここは、抵抗せずに従っておいた方がいい……。[%p]"
msgstr "5700:For now, the smart thing to do would be to not resist.[%p]"

msgid "5800:僕は観念して、セナの前に立った。[%p]"
msgstr "5800:I gave up and walked over to Sena.[%p]"

msgid "5900:思わず立ち止まってしまった。[%p]"
msgstr "5900:Suddenly, I stopped.[%p]"

msgid "6000:あからさまな命令口調。[linebreak]しかも、まるでこの電車が自分の持ち物みたいな言い方だ。[%p]"
msgstr "6000:There was a note of command in her voice. It was like this train car was her personal possession.[%p]"

msgid "6100:もちろん僕には入るつもりなんてなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "6100:Of course, I didn't have any intention of going inside.[%p]"

msgid "6200:この女の正体が分からないし、怖いし、三次元女とふたりきりで話すのも苦手だし。[%p]"
msgstr "6200:I didn't know who this girl was, and I could barely talk to 3D girls anyway.[%p]"

msgid "6300:関わり合いになりたくない。[%p]"
msgstr "6300:I didn't want to get involved.[%p]"

msgid "6400:[name]セナ[line]「入れ、と言っている」[%p]"
msgstr "6400:[name]セナ[line]I said come in.[%p]"

msgid "6500:セナは有無を言わせない態度だった。[%p]"
msgstr "6500:Sena's voice was commanding and brooked no dissent.[%p]"

msgid "6600:微動だにしないけど、僕が少しでも逃げようという素振りを見せればなにをしでかすか分からない。[%p]"
msgstr "6600:She wasn't moving, but if I made the slightest move to run, there was no telling what she'd do.[%p]"

msgid "6700:こいつ、もしかすると相当のＤＱＮかも。[linebreak]男に平気で暴力を振るいそうだ。[%p]"
msgstr "6700:She might be a really high-level DQN. The kind who wouldn't think twice about getting violent with a man.[%p]"

msgid "6800:怖い……。[%p]"
msgstr "6800:I was scared.[%p]"

msgid "6900:だけど、従順なところを少しでも見せたら相手を図に乗らせてしまう。[%p]"
msgstr "6900:But if I was obedient, it just might make things even worse.[%p]"

msgid "7000:これまでにも何度かＤＱＮに絡まれたことはある。[%p]"
msgstr "7000:I'd had to deal with DQNs a few times in my life.[%p]"

msgid "7100:そういう場合、一番いいのは逃げることなんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "7100:The best thing to do was always to run.[%p]"

msgid "7200:逆らおうと従おうと、その後にはどっちにしろひどい目に遭わされるんだから、それなら逃げるのが最善の策なんだ。なんとか隙を見て――[%p]"
msgstr "7200:Whether you did what they said or not, something awful always ended up happening to you. So, the best thing to do was to run. I needed to find a way to get out of here.[%p]"

msgid "7300:[name]拓巳[line]「っ！？」[%p]"
msgstr "7300:[name]拓巳[line]?![%p]"

msgid "7400:いきなり、背中を突き飛ばされた。[%p]"
msgstr "7400:Suddenly, something pushed me forward.[%p]"

msgid "7500:不意を突かれて踏ん張ることもできず、僕は無様にも車内に転がるようにして倒れ込む。[%p]"
msgstr "7500:I was caught off guard and lost my balance, falling forward like an idiot into the train.[%p]"

msgid "7600:呆然としつつ、いったい誰が押したのかと入り口の方を振り返ってみた。[%p]"
msgstr "7600:Shocked, I turned toward the entrance to see who'd pushed me.[%p]"

msgid "7700:電車のすぐ外には、待ち合わせ中と思われる人たちはたくさんいるけど、その中の誰が犯人なのかは特定できない。[%p]"
msgstr "7700:There were a lot of people outside, but I couldn't tell which one of them it had done it.[%p]"

msgid "7800:もしかしたらもう逃げていったのかもしれない。[%p]"
msgstr "7800:Maybe they'd already run away.[%p]"

msgid "7900:どうして僕が突き飛ばされなくちゃいけないんだ？[%p]"
msgstr "7900:Why did they push me, though?[%p]"

msgid "8000:誰がこんなひどいことしたんだ……？[%p]"
msgstr "8000:Who'd do something so mean?[%p]"

msgid "8100:倒れたときに膝を打ったらしく、少し痛む。[%p]"
msgstr "8100:I'd hit my knee when I'd fallen, and it hurt a little.[%p]"

msgid "8200:セナとは目を合わせないようにしながら、僕はヨロヨロと立ち上がった。[%p]"
msgstr "8200:I slowly staggered to my feet, being careful not to look Sena in the eye.[%p]"

msgid "8300:[name]拓巳[line]「あ……れ……？」[%p]"
msgstr "8300:[name]拓巳[line]Huh?[%p]"

msgid "8400:ふと気が付いた。[%p]"
msgstr "8400:Suddenly, I realized something.[%p]"

msgid "8500:ほんの一瞬前までセナの足許にあった鎖の束が、きれいさっぱり消え去ってしまっている。[%p]"
msgstr "8500:The coiled chain that had been at Sena's feet just a moment ago was now completely gone.[%p]"

msgid "8600:どこかに移動させたのかと思ったけど、そんな音はしなかったしセナはさっきからシートに座ったままだ。[%p]"
msgstr "8600:She must've moved it somewhere, but I hadn't heard any sound, and she'd been sitting in her seat the whole time.[%p]"

msgid "8700:そもそも移動させたとして、いったいどこへ？[%p]"
msgstr "8700:And even if she had moved it, where had she moved it to?[%p]"

msgid "8800:車内のどこにも、あの鎖は見当たらない。[%p]"
msgstr "8800:I couldn't see the chain anywhere in the car.[%p]"

msgid "8900:[name]セナ[line]「エラーはどこにあった？」[%p]"
msgstr "8900:[name]セナ[line]Where was the error?[%p]"

msgid "9000:そんな僕の戸惑いなどまったく気にしようとせず、セナはまた意味不明なことを問いかけてくる。[%p]"
msgstr "9000:Sena asked me another strange question, completely ignoring my confusion.[%p]"

msgid "9100:[name]セナ[line]「だから私をつけてきたんじゃないのか？」[%p]"
msgstr "9100:[name]セナ[line]That's why you followed me, right?[%p]"

msgid "9200:僕が戸惑いながらも必死で首を左右に振ると、セナは表情をいっそう険しくした。[%p]"
msgstr "9200:I shook my head quickly in confusion, and her expression only grew sterner.[%p]"

msgid "9300:そしてようやく僕から目をそらし、小さくため息をついてアイスを一口かじった。[%p]"
msgstr "9300:Finally, she looked away from me, sighing a little and nibbling on her popsicle.[%p]"

msgid "9400:彼女の、人を殺せるんじゃないかと思えるほどの視線から解放されて、僕もまたその場にへたり込みそうになった。[%p]"
msgstr "9400:When she released me from her terrible gaze, I almost collapsed.[%p]"

msgid "9500:できればシートに座りたかったけど、それをすることでまたこの女になにか言われやしないかと思うと、結局行動に移すことができない。[%p]"
msgstr "9500:I wanted to sit on a seat, but she'd probably say something. I gave up on the idea.[%p]"

msgid "9600:[name]セナ[line]「お前が私をつけてきているのには気付いていた」[%p]"
msgstr "9600:[name]セナ[line]I realized you were following me.[%p]"

msgid "9700:[name]セナ[line]「私が作ったエラーが見えていただろう？」[%p]"
msgstr "9700:[name]セナ[line]You saw the error I created, right?[%p]"

msgid "9800:[name]拓巳[line]「だ、だからエラーってなに……？」[%p]"
msgstr "9800:[name]拓巳[line]W-What do you mean, error?[%p]"

msgid "9900:[name]セナ[line]「鎖だ。白い鎖」[%p]"
msgstr "9900:[name]セナ[line]The chain. The white chain.[%p]"

msgid "10000:それなら見えた。あの不自然な鎖をたどってここまで来たんだから。[%p]"
msgstr "10000:If that was what she meant, then yes, I'd seen it. I'd followed that strange white chain all the way here.[%p]"

msgid "10100:[name]拓巳[line]「で、でもどこにもない。き、消えたよ……」[%p]"
msgstr "10100:[name]拓巳[line]B-But it's gone. It disappeared.[%p]"

msgid "10200:[name]セナ[line]「消した。私の妄想だからな」[%p]"
msgstr "10200:[name]セナ[line]I got rid of it. It was my delusion, after all.[%p]"

msgid "10300:妄想？　なにを言ってるんだ？[%p]"
msgstr "10300:Delusion? What was she talking about?[%p]"

msgid "10400:[name]拓巳[line]「じゃ、じゃあ、剣は？」[%p]"
msgstr "10400:[name]拓巳[line]T-Then what about the sword?[%p]"

msgid "10500:[name]セナ[line]「お前も持っているだろ？」[%p]"
msgstr "10500:[name]セナ[line]You have one too, right?[%p]"

msgid "10600:はあ？　僕が持ってるって？　持ってるわけないだろ！[linebreak]ダメだ、会話が噛み合わない……。[%p]"
msgstr "10600:Huh? She thought I had one? Of course I didn't! This conversation wasn't making any sense.[%p]"

msgid "10700:[name]セナ[line]「それより――」[%p]"
msgstr "10700:[name]セナ[line]More importantly...[%p]"

msgid "10800:[name]セナ[line]「お前は何者なんだ？」[%p]"
msgstr "10800:[name]セナ[line]Who are you?[%p]"

msgid "10900:[name]セナ[line]「“見えている”みたいだけど」[%p]"
msgstr "10900:[name]セナ[line]You seem to be able to “see.”[%p]"

msgid "11000:[name]拓巳[line]「は……？」[%p]"
msgstr "11000:[name]拓巳[line]What?[%p]"

msgid "11100:セナはチラリと僕を一瞥してから、すぐに窓の外へと顎をしゃくるようにした。[%p]"
msgstr "11100:Sena glanced at me before jerking her head in the direction of the window.[%p]"

msgid "11200:[name]セナ[line]「この窓の外になにが見える？」[%p]"
msgstr "11200:[name]セナ[line]What do you see outside the window?[%p]"

msgid "11300:窓の外って……。[%p]"
msgstr "11300:Outside the window?[%p]"

msgid "11400:人だ。人がいっぱいいる。[%p]"
msgstr "11400:People. I saw lots of people.[%p]"

msgid "11500:さっきよりさらに増えているような気がする。[%p]"
msgstr "11500:There were even more than there'd been a second ago.[%p]"

msgid "11600:それを見るだけで頭が痛くなってきそうだ。[%p]"
msgstr "11600:Just looking at them made my head hurt.[%p]"

msgid "11700:うなだれてケータイをいじっている人、笑顔で電話している人、ボーッと人の流れを眺めている人……窓から見えるのはほとんどが待ち合わせのためにその場にたたずんでいる人たちだった。[%p]"
msgstr "11700:People with their heads down playing with their cellphones, people laughing as they talked on the phone, people just standing and watching other people go by... most of the people I could see from where I was standing seemed to be waiting for someone else.[%p]"

msgid "11800:っていうか、こんなに人がいるのに、僕とセナがこの電車に閉じ込められていることを、どうして誰も変だって思わないんだろう。[%p]"
msgstr "11800:Wait, if there were so many people out there, how come none of them thought it was strange that Sena and I were locked inside the train?[%p]"

msgid "11900:みんな、この電車に注意を向けようとすらしない。[%p]"
msgstr "11900:None of them were paying the train even the slightest bit of attention.[%p]"

msgid "12000:っていうか、こんなに人がいるのに、どうしてさっきから誰もこの電車の中に入ってこないんだろう。[%p]"
msgstr "12000:Actually, how come none of these people actually tried to come inside the train?[%p]"

msgid "12100:[name]セナ[line]「完璧な世界が、そこにあると思うか？」[%p]"
msgstr "12100:[name]セナ[line]Do you think there's a perfect, complete world out there?[%p]"

msgid "12200:[name]セナ[line]「あるはずがない。エラーは確かに存在する」[%p]"
msgstr "12200:[name]セナ[line]That's impossible. There are errors. They exist.[%p]"

msgid "12300:[name]セナ[line]「すべてのものは……人も含めて、電気仕掛けだからな」[%p]"
msgstr "12300:[name]セナ[line]Because everything... humans included... runs on electricity.[%p]"

msgid "12400:それなんて中２病設定？[%p]"
msgstr "12400:Was this her weird, personal fanfiction?[%p]"

msgid "12500:僕もよく似たようなことは考える。[%p]"
msgstr "12500:I mean, I had similar fantasies all the time.[%p]"

msgid "12600:中２病設定がダメだと言うつもりもない。[%p]"
msgstr "12600:I wasn't going to tell her not to have them.[%p]"

msgid "12700:だって世の中に溢れている小説だって映画だってアニメだって、中２病設定ばかりじゃないか。[%p]"
msgstr "12700:All the novels, all the movies, all the anime in the world came from goofy fantasies.[%p]"

msgid "12800:どうして小説家や映画監督の考えた中２病設定はよくて、僕みたいな素人が考えた中２病設定はバカにされるんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "12800:So why were the fantasies of a novelist or a director okay, while the ones amateurs like me came up with were mocked?[%p]"

msgid "12900:それにもっとよく考えてみろ。[linebreak]世界の偉人たちは明らかに中２病だよ。[%p]"
msgstr "12900:And what's more, think about it... All the great people of history had goofy, childish fantasies.[%p]"

msgid "13000:ライト兄弟は１００年も前の時代に“空も飛べるはず”なんて本気で考えてたんだぞ。[%p]"
msgstr "13000:The Wright brothers honestly believed they could fly over a hundred years ago.[%p]"

msgid "13100:ナポレオンは“私の辞書に不可能という文字はない”って豪語しちゃったんだぞ。[%p]"
msgstr "13100:Napoleon actually told people, “The word ‘impossible’ is not in my dictionary.”[%p]"

msgid "13200:だから中２病はバカにされるべきものじゃない。[linebreak]偉人たち誰もが通ってきた道なんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "13200:You shouldn't make fun of somebody for having fantasies. All of history's greats had fantasies.[%p]"

msgid "13300:ただ……問題なのは、なんでこの女が突然僕に中２病設定を披露し始めたんだろうっていうこと……。[%p]"
msgstr "13300:The problem was... this girl had suddenly started sharing hers with me.[%p]"

msgid "13400:[name]セナ[line]「なにを見ているか、じゃない。なにを見せられているか、だ」[%p]"
msgstr "13400:[name]セナ[line]What you see doesn't matter. What matters is what you're being shown.[%p]"

msgid "13500:[name]セナ[line]「人は、身体の外からの情報を五感によって得ているけど、その受け取る情報のおよそ８０パーセントは、視覚から入ってくるんだ」[%p]"
msgstr "13500:[name]セナ[line]People receive information about the outside world from their senses. Over 80% of that information comes from vision.[%p]"

msgid "13600:[name]セナ[line]「そして視覚から得られた映像は、パルス信号となって視神経を通り、脳に送られる」[%p]"
msgstr "13600:[name]セナ[line]The images your vision shows you are transmitted by optic nerves to the brain in the form of electrical pulses.[%p]"

msgid "13700:電話と似たようなものか、とぼんやり思った。[%p]"
msgstr "13700:It was kind of like a phone, I thought.[%p]"

msgid "13800:電話は、声を電気信号に変換してその情報を遠く離れたところに送る。[%p]"
msgstr "13800:A phone took somebody's voice and turned it into an electrical signal, and then sent that information to someone else far away.[%p]"

msgid "13900:[name]セナ[line]「電話か。似ていると言えなくもない」[%p]"
msgstr "13900:[name]セナ[line]A phone, huh? It's similar, in a way.[%p]"

msgid "14000:[name]拓巳[line]「……っ」[%p]"
msgstr "14000:[name]拓巳[line]...[%p]"

msgid "14100:心を読まれた！？[%p]"
msgstr "14100:She read my mind![%p]"

msgid "14200:いや、そんなはずない。[linebreak]また知らず知らずのうちに独り言をつぶやいちゃってた……？[%p]"
msgstr "14200:No, that was impossible. Had I spoken aloud without realizing it again?[%p]"

msgid "14300:[name]セナ[line]「ＶＲ技術を知っているか？」[%p]"
msgstr "14300:[name]セナ[line]Do you know about VR technology?[%p]"

msgid "14400:ヴァーチャルリアリティ……？[%p]"
msgstr "14400:Virtual Reality?[%p]"

msgid "14500:もちろん実際には声に出して答えることはしなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "14500:Of course, this time I was careful not to say it aloud.[%p]"

msgid "14600:[name]セナ[line]「ヴィジュアル・リビルディング」[%p]"
msgstr "14600:[name]セナ[line]Visual Rebuilding.[%p]"

msgid "14700:あれ、違った……。[linebreak]聞いたことないぞ。[%p]"
msgstr "14700:Huh? I was wrong. I'd never heard of that.[%p]"

msgid "14800:[name]セナ[line]「アメリカの精神生理学分野で研究が行われている技術だ」[%p]"
msgstr "14800:[name]セナ[line]It's a technology being researched by American psychophysiologists.[%p]"

msgid "14900:[name]セナ[line]「生まれながらに目が不自由な人でも、目の前にある景色がちゃんと見えるようになる。ビデオカメラのような映像機器を介してな」[%p]"
msgstr "14900:[name]セナ[line]Take someone who's been blind from birth, and make it so they can see what's in front of them. It uses a tool similar to a video camera, you see.[%p]"

msgid "15000:[name]セナ[line]「どうやって、という顔をしているな。だが仕組みとしては単純な話だ」[%p]"
msgstr "15000:[name]セナ[line]You're wondering how that's possible, but the principle is quite simple.[%p]"

msgid "15100:[name]セナ[line]「ビデオカメラが映した映像も、脳を流れる[color index="A0FF0000"]神経パルス[color index="800000"]も、どちらも突き詰めれば電気による信号なんだぞ」[%p]"
msgstr "15100:[name]セナ[line]The video recorded by a camera and a human [color index="A0FF0000"]nerve impulse[color index="800000"] are both, at their most fundamental level, electrical signals.[%p]"

msgid "15200:[name]セナ[line]「要は、神経パルスにコンバートできる技術さえあればいい」[%p]"
msgstr "15200:[name]セナ[line]All you need is something to convert the video into nerve impulses.[%p]"

msgid "15300:[name]セナ[line]「すでに実際にテストは成功している。ある研究チームが特許を取得済みだ」[%p]"
msgstr "15300:[name]セナ[line]They've already succeeded in tests. One research team already has a patent.[%p]"

msgid "15400:特許って……。[linebreak]ホントかな？[%p]"
msgstr "15400:A patent... Was that true?[%p]"

msgid "15500:けっこう細かい部分までうまく設定されてる妄想だとは思うけど、特許とかまで出てきちゃったらさすがに無理があるんじゃないか？[%p]"
msgstr "15500:It felt like a really well-thought-out delusion, but what kind of delusion includes stuff about patents?[%p]"

msgid "15600:[name]セナ[line]「その特許から読み取れることがある」[%p]"
msgstr "15600:[name]セナ[line]If you read the patent carefully, you'll discover something.[%p]"

msgid "15700:ずっと窓の外を見ていたセナが、僕の方へ向き直った。[%p]"
msgstr "15700:Sena turned her gaze away from the window and toward me.[%p]"

msgid "15800:ゆっくりと足を組み替える。[%p]"
msgstr "15800:She crossed her legs again, slowly.[%p]"

msgid "15900:[name]セナ[line]「ある意図的な情報を、[linebreak]神経パルスへコンバートすることが可能なら――」[%p]"
msgstr "15900:[name]セナ[line]If it were possible to convert a certain deliberately-chosen information pattern into nerve impulses...[%p]"

msgid "16000:[name]セナ[line]「人の五感すべて、さらには人の意志そのものもコントロールできるんじゃないか？」[%p]"
msgstr "16000:[name]セナ[line]You would be able to control all five of a person's senses, and in fact, their will itself.[%p]"

msgid "16100:[name]拓巳[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "16100:[name]拓巳[line]...[%p]"

msgid "16200:渋谷駅の目の前にあるのに、この電車内は妙に静かだ。音が遮断されているような感じ。[%p]"
msgstr "16200:The train was right in front of Shibuya Station, but it was strangely quiet. It felt like the sound was being shut out.[%p]"

msgid "16300:もちろん錯覚だろうけど……どうしても、数日前のあの“無人になった渋谷”の妄想を思い出しちゃって、僕は窓の外で動く人混みから目を離せない。[%p]"
msgstr "16300:Of course, it was just my imagination... but I remembered the empty Shibuya I'd seen days ago, and couldn't take my eyes off the crowd outside.[%p]"

msgid "16400:[name]セナ[line]「さっき言ったように、人は電気仕掛けだ」[%p]"
msgstr "16400:[name]セナ[line]Like I said before, people run on electricity.[%p]"

msgid "16500:[name]セナ[line]「脳だけじゃなく、全身に張り巡らされている神経にも、電気が通っている」[%p]"
msgstr "16500:[name]セナ[line]Electricity travels not just through the brain, but all the nerves in the body.[%p]"

msgid "16600:[name]セナ[line]「つまり、肉体的な動きまでも操れるということになるんだ。理論的にはな」[%p]"
msgstr "16600:[name]セナ[line]In other words, you could control their movements as well. Theoretically, that is.[%p]"

msgid "16700:この女……[%p]"
msgstr "16700:This girl...[%p]"

msgid "16800:僕はあ然としてしまった。[%p]"
msgstr "16800:I was in shock.[%p]"

msgid "16900:この女は、僕や優愛なんかよりもよっぽど、妄想癖が強い。[%p]"
msgstr "16900:She was more delusional than even Yua or me.[%p]"

msgid "17000:言ってることはなんとなく論理的に聞こえるけど、明らかに夢物語じゃないか。[%p]"
msgstr "17000:What she said sounded logical on the surface, kind of, but it was clearly just a fantasy.[%p]"

msgid "17100:[name]セナ[line]「事実、特許を取得した研究チームもその方向へと研究内容をシフトしている」[%p]"
msgstr "17100:[name]セナ[line]In fact, the team that got the patent is shifting their research in that direction.[%p]"

msgid "17200:[name]セナ[line]「あまりに危険すぎる内容だったから、アメリカ大統領が歯止めをかけようとして行政命令を出したくらいだ」[%p]"
msgstr "17200:[name]セナ[line]The concept is so dangerous that the American president issued an executive order to try to stop it.[%p]"

msgid "17300:この女の言っていることはどこからどこまでがホントなんだ？[%p]"
msgstr "17300:How much of what she was saying was actually true?[%p]"

msgid "17400:[name]セナ[line]「いかなる機関であろうと、政府との事前合意なしに人体の機密の研究を行うことを禁じる。それを支援することも同様である……とな」[%p]"
msgstr "17400:[name]セナ[line]The order banned any organization from researching the secrets of the human body without prior approval from the government. The same goes for providing any such organization with support.[%p]"

msgid "17500:セナはうつむくと、自らの膝の上に置いていた手をきつく握りしめた。[%p]"
msgstr "17500:Sena looked down. She tightly clenched her fists as they rested in her lap.[%p]"

msgid "17600:[name]セナ[line]「だが世の中は、腐った連中ばかりだ」[%p]"
msgstr "17600:[name]セナ[line]But the world is full of scum.[%p]"

msgid "17700:[name]セナ[line]「倫理を無視して、自分の利益の為だけに他者を平気で犠牲にするような連中がな」[%p]"
msgstr "17700:[name]セナ[line]The kind of scum who'll ignore ethics of any kind, and think nothing of sacrificing others for their own gain.[%p]"

msgid "17800:[name]セナ[line]「反吐が出る」[%p]"
msgstr "17800:[name]セナ[line]It makes me want to throw up.[%p]"

msgid "17900:そう悪態をつくと、溶けかけたガルガリ君の最後の欠片を口に入れ、不意に立ち上がった。[%p]"
msgstr "17900:She put the last of the melting Garugari-kun popsicle into her mouth, then stood up.[%p]"

msgid "18000:僕は思わず後ずさったけど、すぐ後ろがもう壁だった。[%p]"
msgstr "18000:I stepped back, only to find my back against the wall.[%p]"

msgid "18100:[name]セナ[line]「無知は罪だ。“知らない方が幸せなこともある”という人間もいるが、そんなのはただの甘えだ」[%p]"
msgstr "18100:[name]セナ[line]Ignorance is a sin. Some people say it's bliss, but they're[linebreak]naïve.[%p]"

msgid "18200:[name]セナ[line]「世界を疑え。仕組みを知れ」[%p]"
msgstr "18200:[name]セナ[line]Doubt the world. Learn how it works.[%p]"

msgid "18300:[name]セナ[line]「この世界は完璧じゃない」[%p]"
msgstr "18300:[name]セナ[line]This world isn't perfect.[%p]"

msgid "18400:僕の方に向かってくる。[%p]"
msgstr "18400:She was walking toward me.[%p]"

msgid "18500:殴られるかも、と思って顔を腕でかばうようにしたけど、セナはなにもせず僕の横をすり抜けていった。[%p]"
msgstr "18500:I thought she might punch me, and tried to shield myself with my arms. But Sena just walked straight past me.[%p]"

msgid "18600:[name]セナ[line]「――お前の見ている景色は、本物か？」[%p]"
msgstr "18600:[name]セナ[line]Is what you're seeing truly real?[%p]"

msgid "18700:すれ違いざまに僕の方を見ないままそうつぶやき――[%p]"
msgstr "18700:She whispered as she passed me, without so much as a glance my way.[%p]"

msgid "18800:ひとりでさっさと電車から出ていってしまった。[%p]"
msgstr "18800:And then she left the train.[%p]"

msgid "18900:閉じたときと同様に、出入り口の扉はいつの間にか音もなく開いていた。[%p]"
msgstr "18900:Just like when it closed, the door had silently opened again at some point in our conversation.[%p]"

msgid "19000:まるで、狐につままれたような気分だ。[%p]"
msgstr "19000:The whole conversation felt like a strange dream, like maybe it had never happened at all.[%p]"

msgid "19100:僕は、去っていくセナの後ろ姿を窓越しに呆然と見送る。[linebreak]彼女はまったく振り返ろうとせずに足早に人の波の中へと消えていった。[%p]"
msgstr "19100:I watched Sena walk away through the train car's window, standing there in shock. She disappeared into the crowd without turning around once.[%p]"

msgid "19200:結局、あの女がなにを言いたかったのか、さっぱり理解できなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "19200:In the end, I never did figure out what she was trying to say.[%p]"

msgid "19300:分かったのは、セナが世界を憎んでいるっていうことぐらい。[linebreak]まさに典型的中２病。[%p]"
msgstr "19300:The one thing I could tell was that she really hated the world. A completely typical teenager, I guess.[%p]"

msgid "19400:僕としては、一方的に毒デンパを垂れ流されていい迷惑だよ。[%p]"
msgstr "19400:From my perspective, having to listen to all that crazy stuff was just a nuisance.[%p]"

msgid "19500:口調が口調だけに、まるで講義を受けているみたいだった。[%p]"
msgstr "19500:The way she spoke made it sound like she was a teacher giving a lecture.[%p]"

msgid "19600:あの話し方は、２次元なら萌え要素のひとつとしてアリだけど、リアルだとＤＱＮぽさが強調されるだけだな。[%p]"
msgstr "19600:In 2D, the way she talked might be kind of moe, but in the real world it just made her seem like a DQN.[%p]"

msgid "19700:でも、襲われなくてホッとした。[%p]"
msgstr "19700:But... I was glad she didn't attack me.[%p]"

msgid "19800:あの女からは、なぜだか誰彼構わずひっぱたいてきそうな雰囲気を感じる。[%p]"
msgstr "19800:For some reason, she had this air about her like she might slap someone at any time, for any reason.[%p]"

msgid "19900:一息つきたくて、さっきまでセナが座っていたシートに腰を下ろす。[%p]"
msgstr "19900:I felt like I needed to rest for a moment, so I sat down in the seat where Sena had been sitting a moment ago.[%p]"

msgid "20000:その直後、いきなりＤＱＮぽいカップルが車内に入ってきた。[%p]"
msgstr "20000:A second later, a DQN-looking couple came inside.[%p]"

msgid "20100:さらにその後にはこれも見るからにＤＱＮのコギャル三人組、[linebreak]そして初老のおっさん、スーツを着た若いサラリーマンまでが続く。[%p]"
msgstr "20100:Then soon after them, three DQN-looking girls came in. Then an old man, and a young salaryman in a suit.[%p]"

msgid "20200:あっと言う間に、車内は窮屈になった。[%p]"
msgstr "20200:Before long at all, the car was jammed tight with people.[%p]"

msgid "20300:セナが出ていく前までは誰も入ってこようとしなかったのに、急になんなんだ？[%p]"
msgstr "20300:Nobody had tried to come in when Sena was here, so why had it suddenly changed?[%p]"

msgid "20400:ＤＱＮカップルとコギャルの声がうるさすぎて、僕は心の中で“氏ね”を連呼しつつ、そそくさとその場から離れた。[%p]"
msgstr "20400:The voices of the girls and DQN couple were annoying me. I whispered “die” several times to myself, silently, before leaving.[%p]"

